3
00:00:10,570 --> 00:00:13,090
And it's also banked.

4
00:00:13,090 --> 00:00:17,590
So this is the overhead
view of our circular track.

5
00:00:17,590 --> 00:00:19,140
It has radius, r.

6
00:00:19,140 --> 00:00:23,280
And here's our car moving
at a constant velocity.

7
00:00:23,280 --> 00:00:26,930
Now, from the side view when
we want to look at that bank

8
00:00:26,930 --> 00:00:29,340
