14
00:00:52,490 --> 00:00:54,990
up or down the inclined plane.

15
00:00:54,990 --> 00:00:56,840
So how should we analyze that?

16
00:00:56,840 --> 00:01:00,240
Well our approach will be to
apply Newton's second laws.

17
00:01:00,240 --> 00:01:02,110
Now what's very
important to realize

18
00:01:02,110 --> 00:01:04,640
