94
00:05:00,900 --> 00:05:05,250
is exactly the square
root of rg tan phi.

95
00:05:05,250 --> 00:05:07,510
And that's how we
analyze the motion

96
00:05:07,510 --> 00:05:08,760
of this car on a banked turn.

97
