until it reaches

114
00:06:15,040 --> 00:06:19,560
a-- as it starts slide
up the inclined plane

115
00:06:19,560 --> 00:06:22,250
it will get to this
new radius, r prime,

116
00:06:22,250 --> 00:06:25,020
but because a car will have
a little inertia it will

117
00:06:25,020 --> 00:06:28,100
